    <h2>OBJECT (4)</h2>

    <pre><code class="language-python">environment = &lt;p5.Environment object&gt;
keyboard = &lt;p5.Keyboard object&gt;
mouse = &lt;p5.Mouse object&gt;
screen = &lt;p5.Screen object&gt;</code></pre>

    <h2>TYPE (8)</h2>

    <pre><code class="language-python">Color = &lt;class 'p5.Color'&gt;
Environment = &lt;class 'p5.Environment'&gt;
